I '''Brigitte Bardot''' (French {{IPA2|bʁiʒit baʁˈdo}}) (born [[September 28]], [[1934]]) metung yang [[w:France|Frances]] a [[artista]], [[modelu]], [[talakanta]], ampong aktibista king katuliran da reng animal. Aniang 2007, pinili ne ning [[Empire (magazine)|Empire]] a metung kareng 100 Sexiest Film Stars.<ref>[http://www.empireonline.com/100sexiest/default.asp?star=98 Empireonline.com] Retrieved December 19, 2007.</ref> 

Kaibat nang migretiru king pamag-artista aniang dekadang 1970, liban neng Bardot ing bayung papil antimong aktibista para king [[w:aniaml rights|katuliran da reng animal]]. Aniang dekadang 1990, megi yang masikan a kritiku ning migrasiun, Islam king Francia, ampong [[w:homosexuality]].<ref name="AnthropologyTodayApr07">Jonathan Benthall ''[http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1467-8322.2007.00494.x Animal liberation and rights]'' [[Anthropology Today]] Volume 23 Issue 2 Page 1 - April 2007</ref>, at mekatalima ne miparusan (''convicted'') uling king "[[Incitement to ethnic or racial hatred|pamagpamua laban kareng aliwang lahi]]" (inciting racial hatred).<ref name = "race fine">{{cite news|title=Bardot fine for stoking race hate|date=2008-06-03|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7434193.stm|accessdate=2008-06-03|publisher=BBC News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bardot fined for racist remarks|date=2000-06-16

